Brookshire Abbey - Hostage Rescue

The Brookshire Abbey in Enoch has been 
taken by terrorists who demand the release
of General Yukiya Amano for the release
of two spiritual leaders. 
 
Counter-Terrorists: Enter the Terrorist
stronghold and rescue the hostages. 
Take out the Terrorists without 
jeopardizing the hostages.

Terrorists: Prevent the Counter-Terrorist
force from rescuing the hostages. 
 
Other Notes: There are 2 hostages in 
this mission and one hostage rescue zone
denoted by a red smoke grenade. 

By: Redbodega
www.redbodega.com
